## 1.5

设 $U = [u_1, u_2, u3]$

则:

$$
U^T M U =
\begin{bmatrix}
\frac{1}{2} \left(17-3 \sqrt{17}\right) c_1^2 m & 0 & 0 \\
0 & \frac{1}{2} \left(3 \sqrt{17}+17\right) c_2^2 m & 0 \\
0 & 0 & c_3^2 L^2 m \\
\end{bmatrix}
$$

$$
U^T K U =
\begin{bmatrix}
-\left(4 \sqrt{17}-17\right) c_1^2 k & 0 & 0 \\
0 & \left(4 \sqrt{17}+17\right) c_2^2 k & 0 \\
0 & 0 & c_3^2 g L m \\
\end{bmatrix}
$$

所以满足正交性

要求

$$U^T M U = I$$

解得

$$
\begin{cases}
c_1 = \frac{\sqrt{2}}{\sqrt{17 m-3 \sqrt{17} m}} = \sqrt {\frac{3 \sqrt{17}+17}{68 m}}\\
c_2 = \frac{\sqrt{2}}{\sqrt{3 \sqrt{17} m+17 m}} = \sqrt {\frac{17-3 \sqrt{17}}{68 m}} \\
c_3 = \frac{1}{L \sqrt{m}}
\end{cases}
$$

此时

$$
U^T K U = \Lambda =
\begin{bmatrix}
\frac{\sqrt{17}-5}{4} \frac{k}{m} & 0 & 0 \\
0 & \frac{\sqrt{17}+5}{4} \frac{k}{m} & 0 \\
0 & 0 & \frac{g}{L}
\end{bmatrix}
$$

## 1.6

令$y = [u_1, u_2, \theta]^T$, 则原方程即为

$$M \ddot y + K y = 0$$

取$U = [u_1, u_2, u3]$, 令$y = U \eta$, 同时方程两端乘以$U^T$

则:

$$\ddot \eta + \Lambda \eta = 0$$

方程解耦为:

$$
\begin{cases}
\ddot{\eta}_1 + \lambda_1 \eta_1 &= 0 \\
\ddot{\eta}_2 + \lambda_2 \eta_2 &= 0 \\
\ddot{\eta}_3 + \lambda_3 \eta_3 &= 0
\end{cases}
$$

解得

$$
\begin{cases}
\eta_1 &= C_{11} \cos \omega_1 t + C_{12} \sin \omega_1 t \\
\eta_2 &= C_{21} \cos \omega_2 t + C_{21} \sin \omega_2 t \\
\eta_3 &= C_{31} \cos \omega_3 t + C_{31} \sin \omega_3 t
\end{cases}
$$

div.data-content:
### a

根据

$$
\begin{cases}
y(0) = [0, 1, 0]^T \\
\dot y(0) = [0, 0, 0]^T
\end{cases}
$$

代入得到

$$
\begin{cases}
\eta(0) = [\sqrt{m + \frac{3m}{\sqrt{17}}}, \sqrt{m - \frac{3m}{\sqrt{17}}}, 0]^T \\
\dot \eta(0) = [0, 0, 0]^T
\end{cases}
$$

可得

$$\eta = \begin{pmatrix}
\sqrt{\frac{3 m}{\sqrt{17}}+m} \cos \omega_1 t \\
\sqrt{m-\frac{3 m}{\sqrt{17}}} \cos \omega_2 t \\
0
\end{pmatrix}$$

所以

$$
\begin{align*}
y &=
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{2} {\sqrt{17}} \cos \omega_1 t - \frac{2} {\sqrt{17}} \cos \omega_2 t\\
\frac{\sqrt{17} + 3}{2 \sqrt{17}}\cos \omega_1 t + \frac{\sqrt{17} - 3}{2 \sqrt{17}}\cos \omega_2 t \\
0
\end{pmatrix} \\
&=
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{2} {\sqrt{17}} \cos \left( \sqrt {\frac{5 - \sqrt{17}}{4 } \frac{k}{m}} t \right) - \frac{2} {\sqrt{17}} \cos \left( \sqrt {\frac{5 + \sqrt{17} }{4 } \frac{k}{m}} t \right)\\
\frac{\sqrt{17} + 3}{2 \sqrt{17}}\cos \left( \sqrt {\frac{5 - \sqrt{17}}{4 } \frac{k}{m}} t \right) + \frac{\sqrt{17} - 3}{2 \sqrt{17}}\cos \left( \sqrt {\frac{5 + \sqrt{17} }{4 } \frac{k}{m}} t \right) \\
0
\end{pmatrix}
\end{align*}
$$

### b

根据

$$
\begin{cases}
y(0) = [1, 0, 1]^T \\
\dot y(0) = [0, 0, 0]^T
\end{cases}
$$

代入得到

$$
\begin{cases}
\eta(0) = [\frac{1}{4} \left(\sqrt{17}-3\right) \sqrt{\frac{3 m}{\sqrt{17}}+m}, -\frac{1}{4} \left(\sqrt{17}+3\right) \sqrt{m-\frac{3 m}{\sqrt{17}}}, L \sqrt{m}]^T \\
\dot \eta(0) = [0, 0, 0]^T
\end{cases}
$$

可得

$$\eta = \begin{pmatrix}
\frac{1}{4} \left(\sqrt{17}-3\right) \sqrt{\frac{3 m}{\sqrt{17}}+m} \cos \omega_1 t \\
-\frac{1}{4} \left(\sqrt{17}+3\right) \sqrt{m-\frac{3 m}{\sqrt{17}}} \cos \omega_2 t \\
L \sqrt{m} \cos \omega_3 t
\end{pmatrix}$$

所以

$$
\begin{align*}
y &=
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{\sqrt{17} - 3}{2 \sqrt{17}} \cos \omega_1 t + \frac{\sqrt{17} + 3}{2 \sqrt{17}} \cos \omega_2 t\\
\frac{1} {\sqrt{17}}\cos \omega_1 t - \frac{1} {\sqrt{17}}\cos \omega_2 t \\
\cos \omega_3 t
\end{pmatrix} \\
&=
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{\sqrt{17} - 3}{2 \sqrt{17}} \cos \left( \sqrt {\frac{5 - \sqrt{17}}{4 } \frac{k}{m}} t \right) + \frac{\sqrt{17} + 3}{2 \sqrt{17}} \cos \left( \sqrt {\frac{5 + \sqrt{17} }{4 } \frac{k}{m}} t \right)\\
\frac{1} {\sqrt{17}}\cos \left( \sqrt {\frac{5 - \sqrt{17}}{4 } \frac{k}{m}} t \right) - \frac{1} {\sqrt{17}}\cos \left( \sqrt {\frac{5 + \sqrt{17} }{4 } \frac{k}{m}} t \right) \\
\cos \left( \sqrt {\frac{g}{L}} t \right)
\end{pmatrix} \\
\end{align*}
$$

### c

根据

$$
\begin{cases}
y(0) = [0, 0, 0]^T \\
\dot y(0) = [1, 1, 0]^T
\end{cases}
$$

代入得到

$$
\begin{cases}
\eta(0) = [0, 0, 0]^T \\
\dot \eta(0) = [\frac{1}{4} \left(\sqrt{17}+1\right) \sqrt{\frac{3 m}{\sqrt{17}}+m}, -\frac{\left(\sqrt{17}-1\right) \sqrt{17 m-3 \sqrt{17} m}}{4 \sqrt{17}}, 0]^T
\end{cases}
$$

可得

$$\eta = \begin{pmatrix}
\frac{\sqrt{1+\frac{3}{\sqrt{17}}} \left(\sqrt{17}+1\right) m }{2 \sqrt{-\left(\left(\sqrt{17}-5\right) k\right)}} \sin \omega_1 t \\
-\frac{\sqrt{1-\frac{4}{\sqrt{17}}} \left(\sqrt{17}-1\right) m }{2 \sqrt{k}} \sin \omega_2 t \\
0
\end{pmatrix}$$

所以

$$
\begin{align*}
y &=
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{\sqrt{31+7 \sqrt{17}} }{\sqrt{34}} \sqrt{\frac{m}{k}}\sin \omega_1 t + \frac{\sqrt{31-7 \sqrt{17}} }{\sqrt{34}} \sqrt{\frac{m}{k}} \sin \omega_2 t\\
\frac{\sqrt{95 + 23 \sqrt{17}} }{\sqrt{34}} \sqrt{\frac{m}{k}}\sin \omega_1 t - \frac{\sqrt{95 - 23 \sqrt{17}} }{\sqrt{34}} \sqrt{\frac{m}{k}} \sin \omega_2 t\\
0
\end{pmatrix} \\
&=
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{\sqrt{31+7 \sqrt{17}} }{\sqrt{34}} \sqrt{\frac{m}{k}}\sin \left( \sqrt {\frac{5 - \sqrt{17}}{4 } \frac{k}{m}} t \right) + \frac{\sqrt{31-7 \sqrt{17}} }{\sqrt{34}} \sqrt{\frac{m}{k}} \sin \left( \sqrt {\frac{5 + \sqrt{17} }{4 } \frac{k}{m}} t \right)\\
\frac{\sqrt{95 + 23 \sqrt{17}} }{\sqrt{34}} \sqrt{\frac{m}{k}}\sin \left( \sqrt {\frac{5 - \sqrt{17}}{4 } \frac{k}{m}} t \right) - \frac{\sqrt{95 - 23 \sqrt{17}} }{\sqrt{34}} \sqrt{\frac{m}{k}} \sin \left( \sqrt {\frac{5 + \sqrt{17} }{4 } \frac{k}{m}} t \right)\\
0
\end{pmatrix}\\
\end{align*}
$$

## 1.7

由题意, 可得

$$
M = \begin{bmatrix}
m & 0 & 0 \\
0 & 4m & 0 \\
0 & 0 & 2m L^2
\end{bmatrix}
$$

$$
K = \begin{bmatrix}
2 k & -k & 0 \\
-k & k & 0 \\
0 & 0 & 2m g L
\end{bmatrix}
$$

特征方程

$$|K - \lambda M | = 2( m L^2 \lambda - m g L) (4 m^2 \lambda^2 - 9 k m \lambda + k^2) = 0$$

解得

$$
\begin{cases}
\lambda_1 &= \frac{9 - \sqrt{65} }{8} \frac{k}{m} \\
\lambda_2 &= \frac{9 + \sqrt{65}}{8} \frac{k}{m} \\
\lambda_3 &= \frac{g}{L} \\
\end{cases}
$$

特征向量为

$$
\begin{cases}
u_1 &= c_1 \begin{bmatrix}
\frac{-7 + \sqrt{65} }{2} \\
1 \\
0
\end{bmatrix} \\
u_2 &= c_2 \begin{bmatrix}
\frac{-7 - \sqrt{65} }{2} \\
1 \\
0
\end{bmatrix} \\
u_3 &= c_3 \begin{bmatrix}
0 \\
0 \\
1
\end{bmatrix} \\
\end{cases}
$$
